        <div style="padding-left: 5px;padding-right: 5px;padding-top: 5px;padding-bottom: 5px;background-color: #f7f7f7;">
            <div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Release: 1.52.2</h3>
                    <p>Deployment date: April 29, 2021</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Enhancements</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Gateways now report the number of active connections. This allows admins to view a gateway's current connection load.</li>
                        <li>
                            <p>The log integrity validation algorithm for SSH session logs has been improved. This helps to ensure the authenticity of SSH session logs.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>A gateway will no longer start if the temporary directory for its log storage is not on a valid device. This allows an invalid log directory to be detected at start up rather than during runtime.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>The temporary directory for gateway log storage can now be specified by the <span class="code">SessionLogTempStorageDirectory</span> configuration option. This allows the temporary directory to be configured and for the temporary directory and storage directory to be on different volumes.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4>Fixes</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <p>SSH session metadata was incorrectly logged.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>